      "raw_text": "WALLA WALA, Wash, April 49,\nAll day yesterday and today 2\nwomen amused themselves with\nfancy needleworll as they sat in\neasy chairs just outside the door Of\nthe United States land Office. They\nwere patiently awaiting their\nchance to file upon some of the land\nwhich will come in for entry Satur-\nday under the Palouse project."
